    <item>
      <title>执政党非洲人国民大会 (ANC) 探索联合执政选项，兰特看跌押注增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/zar-bearish-bets-rise-as-anc-top-brass-discuss-coalition-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在非洲人国民大会领导层着手解决紧迫的联盟建设问题之际，交易员们押注兰特将进一步下跌，此前选举结果与几十年的先例相悖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/zar-bearish-bets-rise-as-anc-top-brass-discuss-coalition-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登纪念诺曼底登陆日 称乌克兰战争威胁民主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-says-democracy-at-risk-in-ukraine-fight-as-he-marks-d-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登对他认为是当今民主威胁的两个人——弗拉基米尔·普京和唐纳德·特朗普——进行了尖锐的斥责，这是美国在反对威权主义方面取得的最伟大的胜利之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-says-democracy-at-risk-in-ukraine-fight-as-he-marks-d-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:22:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国寻求加大对胡塞武装的压力，威胁也门战争停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/us-seeks-to-up-pressure-on-houthis-in-threat-to-yemen-war-truce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其盟友正加大力度阻止红海胡塞武装分子发动船舶袭击，方式是封锁其收入来源，此举可能危及旨在结束也门近十年战争的和平协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/us-seeks-to-up-pressure-on-houthis-in-threat-to-yemen-war-truce</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度法院下令各邦与干旱首都共享水资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/indian-court-orders-states-to-share-water-with-parched-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院周四下令邻近各州增加对首都的供水，以帮助缓解因持续热浪造成的严重缺水现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/indian-court-orders-states-to-share-water-with-parched-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府寻求华尔街如何使用人工智能的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-administration-seeks-input-on-how-wall-street-is-using-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部正在寻求更多有关金融公司如何使用人工智能以及该技术给该行业带来的机遇和风险的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/biden-administration-seeks-input-on-how-wall-street-is-using-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非工会敦促非国大考虑与民主联盟达成公平协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-african-elections-unions-suggest-anc-da-government-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士透露，南非最大的工会联合会正在敦促执政党非洲人国民大会考虑寻求主要反对党的支持，以使其在失去议会多数席位后继续执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-african-elections-unions-suggest-anc-da-government-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
